Package org.training.foodorderapplication.service.implementation

package org.training.foodorderapplication.service.implementation
This package contains the implementation classes for the service interfaces in the Food Order Application.

The package contains the following implementation classes:

AuthenticationServiceImpl - provides implementation for the AuthenticationService interface.

FoodItemQuantityServiceImpl - provides implementation for the FoodItemQuantityService interface.

FoodItemServiceImpl - provides implementation for the FoodItemService interface.

FoodOrderServiceImpl - provides implementation for the FoodOrderService interface.

UserServiceImpl - provides implementation for the UserService interface.

VendorServiceImpl - provides implementation for the VendorService interface.

These implementation classes provide concrete implementations of the service interfaces and are responsible for executing the business logic of the application. By separating the interface and implementation layers of the application, the Food Order Application is able to achieve a separation of concerns and maintain a clear and organized architecture.
